OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFine, but rather windy morning.
OL,6,FSome early brighter or sunny spells
OL,7,Flikely, but otherwise cloudy for most,
OL,8,Fespecially later in the day. Staying
OL,9,Fdry, although the odd shower cannot be
OL,10,Fcompletely ruled out through the
OL,11,Fafternoon. Staying windy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning wet, with heavy and
OL,14,Fgusty rain spreading southeast through
OL,15,Fthe first half of the night, before
OL,16,Fclearing by dawn. The odd clearer
OL,17,Fspell follows into northern parts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
