OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA largely fine day with early
OL,6,Fcloud breaking give some good spells
OL,7,Fof sunshine. Although the odd shower
OL,8,Fis also possible. Chilly, despite
OL,9,Feasing winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFine
OL,12,FSaturday, with brighter or sunny
OL,13,Fspells, light winds, and isolated
OL,14,Fshowers. Fine, dry Sunday, before rain
OL,15,Fspreads east later. Chilly overnight,
OL,16,Fperhaps isolated showers. Breezy, but
OL,17,Fmostly dry Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
